{#
    Qui Sommes-Nous Section — Full-width cinematic background image with overlay text
#}

<section style="position: relative; width: 100%; height: 65vh; min-height: 500px; max-height: 720px; overflow: hidden; display: flex; align-items: center;">

    {# Background Image #}
    <div style="
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        background-image: url('https://cateco.fr/17276-large_default/table-basse-gigogne-memphis-x3.webp');
        background-size: cover;
        background-position: center;
        transform: scale(1.04);
        transition: transform 6s ease;
    " id="about-bg"></div>

    {# Gradient Overlay — dark on left, fades to transparent on right #}
    <div style="
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        background: linear-gradient(
            90deg,
            rgba(15, 15, 15, 0.72) 0%,
            rgba(15, 15, 15, 0.45) 45%,
            rgba(15, 15, 15, 0.08) 100%
        );
    "></div>

    {# Content — left-aligned overlay #}
    <div style="position: relative; z-index: 2; padding: 0 6vw; max-width: 640px;">

        {# Eyebrow label #}
        <p style="
            color: #E87722;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.12em;
            margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
        ">Notre histoire</p>

        {# Headline #}
        <h2 style="
            font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 4.5vw, 3.8rem);
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #ffffff;
            margin: 0 0 1.5rem 0;
            line-height: 1.1;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        ">Qui sommes-nous&nbsp;?</h2>

        {# Body text #}
        <p style="
            font-size: clamp(0.95rem, 1.3vw, 1.1rem);
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.82);
            line-height: 1.75;
            margin: 0 0 2.2rem 0;
            max-width: 480px;
        ">
            Ouvert depuis 2003, Catéco est l'enseigne incontournable des guyanais dans l'équipement
            des maisons, bricolage, jardinage et loisirs et tant d'autres secteurs. C'est le magasin
            des bonnes affaires qui propose toujours des prix agressifs. Son catalogue 124&nbsp;pages
            renouvelé régulièrement propose les produits les plus astucieux et malins.
        </p>

        {# CTA Button #}
        <a href="/qui-sommes-nous"
           style="
               display: inline-flex;
               align-items: center;
               gap: 0.5rem;
               background-color: #E87722;
               color: #ffffff;
               font-weight: 700;
               font-size: 0.95rem;
               padding: 0.85rem 2rem;
               border-radius: 9999px;
               text-decoration: none;
               box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(232, 119, 34, 0.4);
               transition: all 0.3s ease;
           "
           onmouseover="this.style.backgroundColor='#cf6a1e'; this.style.transform='translateY(-2px)'; this.style.boxShadow='0 8px 25px rgba(232,119,34,0.5)'"
           onmouseout="this.style.backgroundColor='#E87722'; this.style.transform=''; this.style.boxShadow='0 4px 20px rgba(232,119,34,0.4)'">
            En savoir plus
            <svg style="width:16px;height:16px;" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/>
            </svg>
        </a>

    </div>

    {# Subtle Ken Burns animation on the background #}
    <style>
        #about-bg {
            animation: kenburns 12s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
        }
        @keyframes kenburns {
            from { transform: scale(1.04) translateX(0); }
            to   { transform: scale(1.08) translateX(-1%); }
        }
    </style>

</section>
